  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. lumbar spondylolisthesis

          2. symptoms of low back pain and/or neurogenic claudication with or without radiculopathy
             referable to the lumbar spine,

          3. at least 3 months of failed conservative therapies

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. multilevel lumbar degenerative diseases

          2. history of previous lumbar surgery
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
